body_html:
I'm on a lower version. Anyone got tips on upgrading. Preferably on anaconda
On 18 Nov 2015 10:06 pm, "Vijay Vasudevan" notifications@github.com wrote:

Most likely the runtime is selecting too old a version of protobuf -- we
require protobuf 3.0.0.a3 or higher.

I'd see if any other installed version of protobuf is somehow interfering.

—
Reply to this email directly or view it on GitHub
#282 (comment)
.
